Libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(plotly)
library(hrbrthemes)
library(skimr)
library(janitor)
library(plotly)

Exploring the data

df<- iris

Data visualization

  • Density plots
  • Boxplots
p1 <- df %>%
  gather(c(1:4),key="key",value="val") %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=val, fill=Species)) + 
  geom_density(alpha=0.5) +
  facet_wrap(~key,scales="free")

p1 <- ggplotly(p1)
p1

Figure 1: Density plots

p2 <- df %>%
  gather(c(1:4),key="key",value="val") %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=Species,y=val,fill=Species)) +
  geom_boxplot() + 
  facet_wrap(~key,scales="free") 

p2 <- ggplotly(p2)
p2
